        "paragraph_index": 1,
        "text": "### Standard Answer from Established Electrochemistry Data\n\nThe standard reduction potential for the Cu²⁺/Cu⁰ couple is well-established:\n\n| Half-Reaction | E° (V vs. SHE) | Conditions |\n|---|---|---|\n| Cu²⁺ + 2e⁻ → Cu⁰ | **+0.342 V** | 25 °C, aqueous, unit activity |\n\n> **Source:** NIST Chemistry WebBook / IUPAC standard tables (not SRD-46).",
